Installation
------------

To compile the DBIngestor library you need the following hard
dependancies:

- Boost library
- cmake

Optional:

- unixODBC / ODBC library
- MySQL Client API
- Sqlite3

To compile:

mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX:PATH=/usr/local/DBIngestor ..
make all
sudo make install

Add library and include path to system PATH variables

To compile the documentation:

doxygen DBIngestor.doxygen